    "Body": "Business Development Working Student SatoshiPay is a fast-growing technology company founded in 2014. We are right in the middle of the nascent Blockchain industry that is reinventing payments, banking, and money. We are looking for a working student to assist our Business Development Managers for the industries publishing and payment. This is an excellent opportunity for a working student to learn about business development in an ambitious startup in one of the most vibrant industries. A steep learning curve is guaranteed! Responsibilities Help the Business Development Managers to identify opportunities that drive growth for the company by evaluating existing and inbound leads and product lines as well as corporate development Assist in elaborating new business cases in different verticals like Fintech, Media, IoT, TelCo Work collaboratively with the Product and Tech departments to execute sales strategies as enhancements are introduced to existing solutions Assist customers\u2019 business and technical teams throughout implementation and be their point of contact. Assist our Customer Support Agents in answering customer support requests Requirements Certificate of enrolment at a University in Berlin in Entrepreneurship, Economics, Marketing or a related field for at least one semester Strong interest in tech, business or payments Experience in researching market trends, targeting relationships and using proven methods to develop business strategies Strong analytical, problem-solving and organisational skills Open & outgoing mentality, yet an excellent team player Tenacity and drive to seek new business and meet or exceed targets Open to working in a fast-paced, international environment Excellent written and oral communication skills in both English and German Willingness to travel Ability to work 10-20 hours/week for at least 6 months Excellent command of office software, ideally GDrive Suite (Sheets, Docs, Slides) Highly motivated to work in the fast-paced startup industry Comfortable with new technologies and a fast learner What we offer Working at a fast-moving company like SatoshiPay means that all your contributions will have a direct impact on the development of the blockchain industry. The SatoshiPay team is well-connected, both in the fintech and the blockchain scene, so you\u2019ll also benefit from being exposed to these communities. Benefits: Productive work environment with flat hierarchies and flexible working hours Support of a highly skilled and down to earth team Modern, hip and well-equipped office in the center of Berlin Free office drinks, snacks and fruits Subsidized lunches and high-end gym membership Optional winter office participation somewhere in the sun \\ How to apply Please apply by sending an email to jobs+bd-working-student@satoshipay.io with the subject line: \u201cBusiness Development Working Student application\u201d with your CV and a short summary of why you think you\u2019d be suitable for the role. Please include: How many hours per week you can work Which week days you would usually be available Company About Careers Press Blog Contact Newsletter Open Source Legal Imprint Publisher Terms Consumer Terms Privacy Founding member Federal German Blockchain Association Made with ?????????????????? in Berlin and London", 
